    recent_notes: "66yo male heavy smoker with cough x2 months. Also reports blood-streaked sputum on occasion. Lost 10 lbs unintentionally. Chest X-ray shows 'possible nodule, recommend CT.' Assessment: Likely prolonged URI in setting of COPD. Follow-up for CT as outpatient.",
