    recent_notes: "34yo female 3 weeks postpartum with worsening depression and suicidal thoughts. Has plan. Psychiatry consulted for admission. Vitals elevated but attributed to anxiety. Assessment: Major depression with suicidal ideation. Admit to psychiatry.",
