    recent_notes: "79yo female with generalized weakness x3 days since her metoprolol was increased from 25mg to 100mg BID for BP control. Feels lightheaded and fatigued. Exam: Bradycardic, hypotensive. Assessment: Likely orthostatic hypotension. Hold BP meds and PT evaluation.",
