    barriers: [],
    recent_notes: "68yo female with right shoulder pain x2 hours. Came on while watching TV. No trauma. Some nausea. Exam: Right shoulder with limited ROM due to pain, no obvious deformity. Assessment: Likely rotator cuff tendinitis. Conservative management.",
